additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Use only as directed. Keep out of reach of children and pets. Avoid contact with skin, eyes and clothes. If eye or skin contact occurs, immediately rinse with plenty of water for 20 minutes. If eye irritation persists, consult a physician. Do not ingest. If swallowed, do not induce vomiting; call a physician or Poison Control Center immediately. Make sure that the product does not interfere with any car instruments and do not install, adjust or remove the device while driving. Do not place if the shape of ventilation is curved or has a big incline. Do not place near heat or open flame.
